A Triangle sandwich is food which heals 6 hitpoints. It is given by the Sandwich lady Random Event. It can also be obtained by pickpocketing the Tower of Life construction workers: 'Black-eye', 'Gummy', 'No fingers', and 'The Guns'. Alternatively, some crates inside the Tower Life can be searched or telekinetic grab can be used on on the sandwich in the Woodcutting Guild.

A sandwich can be placed into a satchel.
